import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Switch, useRouteMatch } from 'react-router-dom'
import PrivateRoute from '../../routes/PrivateRoute'
import { DashboardContentWrapper, DashboardPageLayout } from '../../styled-component/Container.styled'
import ProductContainer from '../ProductContainer'
import ProductContainerDetails from '../ProductDetails'
import FilterComponent from '../Shared-Component/Filter'
import HeaderComponent from '../Shared-Component/HeaderComponent'

const Dashboard = () => {

  const {path} = useRouteMatch()

  React.useEffect(() => { 
    console.log(path,"path")

  },[])

  return (
    <DashboardPageLayout>
      <DashboardContentWrapper>
        <HeaderComponent></HeaderComponent>
        <BrowserRouter>
        <Switch>
          <PrivateRoute exact component={ProductContainer} path={path}  />
          <PrivateRoute  exact component={ProductContainerDetails} path={`${path}/:id`}  />
        </Switch>
        </BrowserRouter>
        
      </DashboardContentWrapper>
    </DashboardPageLayout>
  )
}

export default Dashboard
